# The Basal Ganglia Network (Nengo)
The original Basal Ganglia class (BasalGanglia in network\BasalGangliaNew) was copied from https://github.com/nengo/nengo/blob/main/nengo/networks/actionselection.py.
It is provided here under a GPLv2 license.
We adapted it to create SPBasalGanglia: with the main adaptation being a new matrix for the connection between STN and GPe, formulated by Dr. P. Michael Furlong. 

